aott/analysis/type_analysis/type_inference.runa
Runtime Type Inference Module for AOTT Optimization

This module provides runtime type inference for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Dynamic type profiling and tracking
- Type specialization opportunities
- Polymorphic type analysis
- Type stability detection
- Type transition tracking
- Union type refinement
- Type guard optimization
- Profile-guided type inference
- Type prediction and speculation
- Type hierarchy analysis
- Interface type resolution
- Generic type instantiation tracking
- Type flow analysis
- Cross-tier type information sharing
- Type feedback collection
:End Note

